================================================================================
INTEGRATION READY
================================================================================

The frontend is ready to connect to OpenClaw backend:

1. Frontend sends: POST /api/chat
   {
     "messages": [
       { "role": "user", "content": "transcribed speech" },
       { "role": "assistant", "content": "previous response" }
     ],
     "model": "claude-haiku"
   }

2. Backend receives, processes with OpenClaw agent

3. Backend returns: JSON
   {
     "response": "natural language response from agent"
   }

4. Frontend plays response as speech + displays text

INTEGRATION POINTS:
- Modify fetch URL in index.html if backend on different host
- Ensure CORS headers in backend response
- Handle timeout if OpenClaw processing is slow
- Implement retry logic for resilience

