DEPLOYMENT PATH
================================================================================

1. Frontend Deployment:
   - Serve index.html via HTTPS
   - Ensure secure context for microphone access
   - Set proper CSP headers

2. Backend Deployment:
   - Deploy backend-example.js (or integrate into existing server)
   - Ensure /api/chat endpoint is accessible
   - Configure CORS headers
   - Connect to OpenClaw gateway

3. OpenClaw Integration:
   - Configure gateway URL in backend
   - Test agent responses
   - Monitor latency

4. Verification:
   - Test full voice flow on desktop
   - Test on mobile devices
   - Load test (multiple concurrent users)
   - Error scenario testing

